 E-Trade has even been doing that online for a long time.

29
00:01:08,847 --> 00:01:12,455
 What differentiates stash is the new user experience.

30
00:01:12,455 --> 00:01:15,930
 Automated investing, simple tracking, simplified summaries.

31
00:01:15,930 --> 00:01:19,899
 User experience design really has become a major differentiator between

32
00:01:19,899 --> 00:01:19,899
 success and failure.

